{"tid":2167601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PORI 有關民主派議員是否接受人大委任的民意調查結果一覽","createTime":"2020-08-21T08:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T09:34:01.000Z","uid":96439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d69929a298d0f591d9b5f7399e1d87da65faed4","tid":2167601,"uid":96439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:18:54.000Z","msg":"1.在網上民調中，逾六成自稱民主派支持者反對議員接受委任；一半自稱非民主派支持者<span class=\"large\">支持</span>議員接受委任。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHRRCT2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHRRCT2.png&h=f98e48e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.在電話民調中，共41%受訪者反對議員接受委任（見上圖）。另根據pori在發佈者接受提問時指出，有61%自稱民主派支持者反對接受委任，19%支持接受委任。（見發佈會57:30提到）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKPublicOpinionProgram/videos/801816417242138/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKPublicOpinionProgram%2Fvideos%2F801816417242138%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=7e0a4f71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKPublicOpinionProgram/videos/801816417242138/</a>"},{"pid":"4ac1f9034d8de9002365fd7d629bb65a4e7e5536","tid":2167601,"uid":96439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38c5bd0916fe200a844043dc2ebeb91a6190255b","tid":2167601,"uid":96439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e6df4782ca5db7291a93051c75a99b3a3fcd2cc0","tid":2167601,"uid":170229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"靠建制派拉高支持委任，拉低反對委任。<br />\n<br />\n反共主流要走唔要留應該都已成定局，但如果再做多次，計埋對家個邊，都有可能五五波。<br />\n<br />\n唔知泛民會唔會話要顧及埋建制派意見，堅持委任呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55135a321dfece304b098f2d07b445c98c906197","tid":2167601,"uid":96439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6df4782ca5db7291a93051c75a99b3a3fcd2cc0","tid":2167601,"uid":17022